                                FIGHTING SOCCER

Typed in by PHANTOM LORD (MEDWAY BOYS). Edited by PARASITE.


A fast and furious game of nerve, skill and challenging that will bounce
right out of your monitor!

Battle against ten other countries in this international Olympic tournament
and slide tackle your opponents through five gruelling rounds of intense
play.

Dribble, kick, shoot, head and foul your way to the Olympic trophy - in
FIGHTING SOCCER ... FIGHT TO WIN!!!

ARROW MODE
If keyboard mode is selected the arrow moves around the player showing in
which direction you kick, that is, there is independant movement of the
arrow.

If joystick mode is selected, the arrow will automatically point in the
direction of the player, and therefore the ball will be kicked in that
direction.

GAME CONTROLS

Joystick Port           1 = Player 2
                        2 = Player 1

FIRE                    Player has ball = Short Kick
                        Player has not got ball = Slide
                        Ball in the air = Header

DOUBLE FIRE             Player has ball = Long Kick
                        Player has not got ball = Slide
                        Ball in the air = Header

If in joystick arrpor mode then arrows direction is determined by players
direction.
Otherwise:

PLAYER 1

LEFT                    RIGHT
Amiga = left ALT        left AMIGA

PLAYER 2

Amiga = right AMIGA     right ALT keypad.

Pausing the game
P = toggle pause mode.
ESC = quit.
